---
title: Loaded Couscous and Spiced Chickpea Bowls with Lemon-Tahini Sauce
description: Beautiful and bountiful bowls are the name of the game for tonight's dinner! Crispy double garlic-roasted chickpeas bring big crouton energy to top garlicky pearl couscous, roasted veggies and a creamy lemon-tahini drizzle.

